! Raster Lookup Unit

A LUT/BRAM-backed FPGA primitive that interprets raster coordinates or pixel
symbols as state lookup addresses.

!! Why It Matters

This is a small buildable bridge between display output and verification
logic: pixels become indexable command cells instead of decorative output.

